{"tid":1276123,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果你唔同意昨晚衝進立法會 請進","createTime":"2019-07-02T01:34:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T14:58:55.000Z","uid":30791,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ba8d176b479edc69432432656579dca57233b7db","tid":1276123,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T01:34:05.000Z","msg":"首先 昨天衝進立法會未必係最好的方法 但已經發生左 我地而家要考慮既係之後既事 點做先係對我方最有利 割席一定係差既選項 就算不同意也不要譴責<br />\n<br />\n其次係昨天的行動是有根有據<br />\n先是政府及一眾官員麻木不仁<br />\n再者是政府包庇警員徇私 警察濫用權力 連獨立調查的機會也沒有<br />\n再者 多次和平示威 多種方法也試過 這是迫不得已 是官逼民反<br />\n<br />\n還有就是勿忘記絕望自殺的同路人 政府視而不見 還打算掩蓋真相 這是天理難容 我們背負著他們的遺志 一定要堅持到底<br />\n<br />\n(我建議大家千祈唔好犯法)"},{"pid":"2dd1375f18c245fc25656f2bd3c1cad854bd6957","tid":1276123,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T02:21:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2090d30772d054b520e9e05d13e9c339700e1a90","tid":1276123,"uid":96675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T02:40:01.000Z","msg":"反對既人唔該你問下自己<br />\n再繼續只係上街係咪真係有用<br />\n上過街 佔過龍和 死過人 都可以唔回應<br />\n你答我仲有咩和理非路線？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"587ce7df670b9207c16cd78e455135bf3c500fce","tid":1276123,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T03:31:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e95d1416ba07a59d082263ccedac9343fd11e74c","tid":1276123,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:34:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6819d898842b4896ccfe56a4392268c32cb662a6","tid":1276123,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T06:25:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b12ba41f552ea5989a353697f545cf55f6204ce","tid":1276123,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"